Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.10,Header,,0,0,0,,This is a Gentlemen of the Hàn free fansub.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.82,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,271)\fade(255,0,255,0,550,3450,4800)}Episode 20
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.82,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349,414)\fade(255,0,255,0,550,3450,4800)}Sūn Cè's death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè dominated Jiāngdōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,seizing Lújiāng and gaining vigorous momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once finished, Zhāng Hóng was sent to Xǔchāng\Nto announce their victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But his request to become Grand Marshal angered Cáo Cāo and so it was refused
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and thus Cè harbored concerns in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He always planned on assaulting Xǔdū.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ergo, the Administrator of Wú Commandery,\NXǔ Gòng, clandestinely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.26,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(83,325)\fade(255,0,255,0,460,1620,2220)}Xǔ Gòng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,sent a messenger to Xǔdū,\Ninforming Cáo Cāo of these developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At night, cross the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliver this to Chancellor Cáo in Xǔdū.\NYou must not reveal this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is extremely classified. You ought to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is crossing the river? Hurry, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Administrator of Wu Commandery, Xu Gong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,During the day, I saw Sun Ce drill his army!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I then crossed back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, our men have enough food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can wipe out \NHuáng Zǔ and cut down Liú Biǎo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you would only need to rely on the\NYangtze to protect Jiāngdōng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and thus have no worries of the rest of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù, your views of the world\Nare different from mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, Cao Cao controls the Emperor\Nand thus the warlords as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.55,0:02:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shào has Héběi and \Nis a fierce tiger among others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could I regard Jiāngdōng as the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and take no actions whatsoever?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you vigorously drilled our army yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have come here to\Nmonitor the building of ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible... is it possible that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Report. An envoy of Xu Gong was crossing the river\Nand was detained by our patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sun Ce is brave and valiant, akin to Xiàng Jí.*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:48.48,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,*Xiàng Jí was a powerful warlord\Nwho contributed to the fall of Qín.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The court ought to reward him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and then summon him to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}You must not let him dominate Jiāngdōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}or he will serve as a menace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, the realm is in great chaos,\Nand the warlords are competing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with no grand ambitions\Nwill be subject to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù, what is it about the world that I think of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(104,342)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,1700,2180)}Sūn Cè\NStyled: Bófú
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,General Sun Ce has sent\Nsomeone to give you a message!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,General Sun is hosting a\Nbanquet in Jīng Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and has asked for you, sir, to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me prepare my chariot and horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pack in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Xu, no need to prepare your vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,General Sun already has done that for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, that is-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an immortal! You better kneel down to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Scram! Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What "immortal?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ask who he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the exalted immortal will punish us if we don't kneel! How would that be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! Get down now! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù, don't tell me even you\Nbelieve in those omens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! If you don't get down,\Nyou better get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here! You can't stay here, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Sun Ce of Jiāngdōng!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are none of them kneeling to me?\NThis is extremely detestable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhòngmóu, please task General Chéng Pǔ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to order people to locate the\Nwhereabouts of those suspicious men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Their locations are not of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell General Cheng to capture that sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, just then, it was\Njust the people of the city
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,seeking help from that immortal. That is just a trifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:05.62,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(575,360)\fade(255,0,255,0,375,1940,2300)}Zhāng Zhāo\NStyled: Zǐbù
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, why be angry then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not be angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the exalted lord of this region!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How can the people pledge\Nthemselves to a sorcerer! What is next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to find out that sorcerer's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and his way of bewitching the citizens of the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Exalted madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son provides his respects to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, why do you look so unhappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, why come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been inside too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, I heard people saying that\Nan immortal had come to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said he cured the sick with such precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There were those who asked for predictions and his telepathy is as if he were a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As I have sat by with nothing to do,\NI want to see him for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, the markets are littered so why take a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, how can an "immortal" exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I seldom go out to walk, so I want to expel boredom\Nand have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The folks' words may not always be false.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, there are many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed so, there are many interesting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out! All of you, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...that heard the preachings of that sorcerer\Nand spread them to my mother's ears!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, all of this will be taken care of by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't anger your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You folks, stop hesitating\Nand help our lord to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! If that sorcerer is still here,\NI cannot be at peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can I rest on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to Dāntú Mountain to hunt and amuse myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As to ease my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Back then, on the lofty Shéntíng Ridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I ascended to worship the temple there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}facing the deitious image of Guāngwǔ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and swore an oath before it.
Comment: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure if he is thinking of the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If I can revive my late father's\Nfoundations in Jiāngdōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:29.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I will improve the temple
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and worship at the snake's hours.*
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.98,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,*9-11 A.M, based on the "Earthly Branches"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Today, if Jiāngdōng is in prosperity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I will again improve the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If I am able to reach the summit of Mount Gāo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I will build another temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:46.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}This will inspire the masses to follow me\Nand stand tall and see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:50.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}To eulogize such pioneers, wouldn't it be great?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:12:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord? My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I came one step too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zibu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to improve the temple of Guāngwǔ\Nso people stand tall and see the world every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so that everyone can be able to\Nnever forget such grand ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How severe is his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare hide it. The arrow had poison,\Nwhich has already entered his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He must rest for a hundred days and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My son has suffered from this calamity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,all because of his volatility and arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you can get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A blessing from the exalted Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What blessings from Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am destined to be a hero, not to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Xu Gong's servants be able to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you rest, you will become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For two months, I've told myself at all times to keep my spirits up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your injury has not healed yet.\NYou must go back and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in peril so your mother and I, along with the mansion servants,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,begged on your behalf to an immortal, a prayer for a swift recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too young and volatile. If there is a disaster, your troubles will never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these fall to my personage alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire mansion is also\Nfooling around with these devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Sun Ce, have my destiny, yet some\Nhave asked immortals to bless me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I really detest those evil spirits, sorcerers, and misleading "prophets."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and tear them out!\NDo not let me see them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dares!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are no immortals to help,\Nwould you be here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun Ce's wound slightly recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He heard that Zhang Hong, sent to Xǔchāng to report his victories,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,had an envoy return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He thus swiftly summoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, how many days were you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(125,365)\fade(255,0,255,0,460,1860,2260)}The Envoy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been six days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you return to Xǔchāng?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go back to Xǔchāng tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,General, can you inform Zhang Hong of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would, only that Zibu won't let me speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, your wound hasn't healed yet and you have been playing Go for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the envoy will return to Xǔchāng tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I only ask one thing of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I beseech you, Zibu, to not halt such.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to ask this gentleman:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Cao Cao really fear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, he wouldn't really say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is most certainly not a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao really does fear Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His tent advisors too all follow his Lordship. Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Only what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His Lordship said that he only asked one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I have spoken too much, so I must take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me one last sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope my lord has the strength of 10,000 gold and will get well soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What "strength of 10,000 gold?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you want to provoke me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it that disobeys me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Guō Jiā disobeyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Guo Jia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you will get angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Guo Jia's words really cannot be told to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I take my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, such words have already come out,\N yet you would leave without finishing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it not make our lord even angrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what words they are, please finish before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Guo Jia had heard Cao Cao's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, he was not at all afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that Your Lordship is condescending but unprepared, 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,impatient and lacking in plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and thus, an ignorant brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There is more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He said... Your Lordship would certainly die\Nat the hands of a lout one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, Guo Jia is just an ignorant man!\NHe'll be dead soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But My Lord, you shouldn't become furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:21:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that dunce dare say such!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I vow to capture Xǔchāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Zibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been several days since\NYuan Shao sent his envoy, Chén Zhèn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not report on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You. Quickly leave and inform Master Chen Zhen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that I want to ally with Yuan Shao\Nand attack Cao Cao together on cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommorow, let us summon\Nour generals to the city top.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And tell Master Chen Zhen to leave as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our talk to attack that Cao is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor warned Your Lordship to rest for 100 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, because of this, you became furious, \Nespecially at "strength of 10,000 gold?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, do rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Chen Zhen is Yuan Shao's envoy and shall be the guest of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,After you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone present,\Nincluding the aged ministers and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the fierce generals,  you all founded\NJiāngdōng and followed me in later conquests,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.26,0:24:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,just like Zǐyì.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:32.66,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(118,370)\fade(255,0,255,0,0,2500,2780)}Tàishǐ Cí \NStyled: Zǐyì
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.80,0:24:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He would kill any champions\N on sight in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.53,0:24:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I led Jiāngdōng into a great undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had relied on you all. It is all due to your efforts to have today's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.97,0:24:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Allow me to show my respect to all you nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.92,0:24:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,May Your Lordship recover and\Nlead Jiāngdōng to great fortunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.46,0:24:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.04,0:25:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the troops of Jiāngdōng have enough supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.33,0:25:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The commoners live in peace and work happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.30,0:25:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These developments are indeed gratifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.93,0:25:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.16,0:25:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if one wants to protect Jiāngdōng, \Nthey ought to cherish no ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with no ambitions, however,\Nwill surely be subject to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.41,0:25:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We could join with Yuan Shao and resist Cao Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.05,0:25:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing so would be today's great undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.45,0:25:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, we must think of danger during peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.12,0:25:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We must prepare supplies and troops early.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.83,0:25:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By acquiring warships and storing supplies,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.33,0:25:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we then can head north and besiege Xǔdū.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.41,0:25:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why look out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.98,0:25:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Down there, Immortal Yú Jí is passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.65,0:25:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We generals wish to pay our respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.00,0:26:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... my Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.80,0:26:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that sorcerer again!\NCome with me to bring him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.76,0:26:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.17,0:26:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He used his sorcery to mislead you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.24,0:26:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you and some soldiers are bewitched as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.64,0:27:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues, then how will I\Nhave anyone to seize the realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.12,0:26:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.34,0:27:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.95,0:27:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.46,0:27:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}My lord, this man's surname is Yu, forename Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.86,0:27:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}He travels everywhere to administer medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.12,0:27:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}He has saved many from many illnesses; there is nothing he hasn't seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.85,0:27:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Now he is called an immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.48,0:27:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}My lord, you must not take this lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.89,0:27:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.07,0:27:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get that sorcerer and quickly slice his head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.07,0:27:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone against this will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.10,0:27:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,beheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.14,0:27:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.05,0:27:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.32,0:27:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.96,0:27:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Yu, over the years in Jiāngdōng,\Nhas not committed any crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.83,0:27:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you mustn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.00,0:27:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of him and other sorcerers, I must kill these swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.10,0:27:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,General, can't you see the people below revere Yu Ji ?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.40,0:27:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.79,0:27:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To lose your temper now would be most inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.60,0:27:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, you are all pragmatic.\NWhy be unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.77,0:28:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I must vanquish evil at all costs,\Nas to pacify the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.81,0:28:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,General, we are all united in\Nagreement to plead for his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.11,0:28:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you all want to follow Yu Ji into rebellion?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.99,0:28:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare incite the people into following heresy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.90,0:28:59.62,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606,358)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,4330,4700)}Yú Jí
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.16,0:28:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I can speak on behalf of heaven to rescue millions of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.30,0:29:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never take anything from the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How then is it inciting the people's hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.00,0:29:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take absolutely nothing,\Nthen where do the clothes and food come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.11,0:29:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is clear you are the sly one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.65,0:29:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if I do not punish you,\Ntheir hearts will change into dissent!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.52,0:29:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, cease this!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.29,0:29:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, you know well that killing immortals without just reasons will bring misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.07,0:29:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But your words! How could you dare not trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.34,0:29:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, you should know your child's intentions, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.41,0:29:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My undertaking hasn't been completed;\Nthe empire hasn't been stabilized!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.71,0:29:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This sorcerer has caused disaster, fooled the civil officials into subservience, 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.80,0:29:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and filled the generals with terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.78,0:29:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The people and soldiers all regard him in awe!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.69,0:29:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues, how will my father's unfinished undertaking ever come true by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.83,0:30:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.00,0:30:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Only last time, you showed disdain to the immortal,\Nhence you risked being killed in that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.17,0:30:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... I am really scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.38,0:30:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The assassins of the mountain\Nwere just Xu Gong's retainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.25,0:30:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to blame me for my good intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.25,0:30:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, how could you be so misled now\Nand blame me for trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.42,0:30:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.26,0:30:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My son...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.49,0:30:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,your father then was short-tempered and rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.20,0:30:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not heed others, and as such he died in the mountains by some stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.74,0:30:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This matter is like yesterday. Surely you won't forget such?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.76,0:31:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are an "immortal," why kneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.61,0:33:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.05,0:33:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.95,0:33:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good or bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.82,0:33:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought to inform the Grand Lady Tai and Madam Qiáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.46,0:33:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My rank is of low prestige. This being a grand matter, \NI really do not dare speak lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.27,0:33:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.81,0:33:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the leader, and I command you to tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.22,0:33:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wouldn't dare lie,\Nbut our Lord looks to be at his end.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.69,0:33:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,His Lordship's venom still hasn't healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.06,0:34:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And having an outbrust with such force, the poison surely leaked into his torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.53,0:34:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It infected his heart and lungs.\NThis ailment is already too late to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.57,0:34:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This lowly servant has long received His Lordship's heavy favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.14,0:34:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I only regret I wasn't able to heal him back to full force now!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.10,0:34:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.91,0:34:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot be spared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, summon my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.79,0:34:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhong Mou...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.02,0:35:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhong Mou...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.92,0:36:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.99,0:36:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.76,0:37:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.16,0:37:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.97,0:37:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You should raise yourself up and\Nuphold your father's and my great cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.07,0:37:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.20,0:37:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Mother, I know my years from Heaven are over
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.86,0:38:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and I can no longer serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.94,0:38:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Now I shall entrust my cause to my younger brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.62,0:38:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and I hope you will train him day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.44,0:38:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}My father and I will fade into the past.\N Be sure he doesn't become too idle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.18,0:38:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear thy younger brother is immature\Nand cannot handle big matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.42,0:38:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.60,0:39:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If you are unsure of \Ninternal matters, ask Zhāng Zhāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.92,0:39:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If you are unsure of \Nexternal matters, ask Zhōu Yú.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.85,0:39:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The only pity is that Zhou Yu isn't here himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.25,0:39:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I cannot order him face-to-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.82,0:39:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}You were always there for me for many years, and I have seen your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.40,0:39:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}After my death, you must respect my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.28,0:39:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Please order your younger sister to inform Zhōu the Youth
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.82,0:40:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}that he must strive to assist my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.20,0:40:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Please do not betray me and the love we share!
